          "SAMPLE": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": null,
              "free_text": [
                "Deuterated polyethylene targets (CD2),",
                "approx. 150 mug/cm**2 thick, were used."
              ]
            }
          ],
          "DETECTOR": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": [
                "TELES",
                "IOCH",
                "PS"
              ],
              "free_text": [
                "",
                " The detection setup consisted of six silicon position",
                "sensitive detectors (PSDs).",
                "Two ionization chambers were used as delta-E detectors",
                "to discriminate nitrogen from carbon ions, thus",
                "allowing the distinction between the H-2(O-17,a+N-14)n",
                "and H-2(O-17,a+C-14)p channels."
              ]
            }
          ],
          "FACILITY": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": {
                "facility": [
                  "VDGT"
                ],
                "institute": "2ITYLNS"
              },
              "free_text": [
                " SMP Tandem Van de Graaff accelerator."
              ]
            }
          ],
          "METHOD": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": null,
              "free_text": [
                " Trojan horse method- Reaction H-2(O-17,a+N-14)n"
              ]
            },
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": [
                "EDE"
              ],
              "free_text": [
                ""
              ]
            }
          ],
          "COMMENT": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": null,
              "free_text": [
                "*By authors*.The present study of the O-17(P,A)N-14",
                "reaction was performed in the energy window",
                "relevant to astrophysics by selecting the QF",
                "contribution to the H-2(O-17,N-14+a)n reaction.",
                "The deuteron was used as the Trojan Horse nucleus",
                "because of its p-n structure; the proton is brought",
                "into the nuclear field of o-17, while the neutron acts",
                "like a spectator to the binary quasifree reaction."
              ]
            }
          ],
          "STATUS": [
